<CENTER><H1><P>
Texture-Maps</H1><P>
<P>
<I>Various images (ok only two.  But you can always send me more)</I><P>
</CENTER><P>
TIFF images to be used with shaders that can handle texture-maps.  Remember, if you are using Pixar's prman you will need to first convert  it into its &quot;texture-map&quot; format before it can be used.<P>
<P>
So far there are only two texture-maps (and they are sort of the same and yet different).  <P>
<P>
